prodNameC: 迪斯爾完整絨毛膜促性腺激素酵素免疫分析套組
ingredientsDesc:
Anti-hCG-Coated Microtitration Strips：coated with anti-hCG antibody.
I-hCG Standard A/Sample Diluent：containing 0 mIU/mL I-hCG in equine serum with sodium azide as a preservative.
I-hCG Standards B-G：containing concentrations of approximately 3, 10, 30, 100, 300 and 1000 mIU/mL I-hCG in equine serum with sodium azide as a peservative.
I-hCG Controls：containing low and high concentrations of I-hCG in equine serum with sodium azide as a preservative.
Assay Buffer：(Green)：containing a protein-based (BSA) buffer with a  non-mercury preservative.
I-hCG Antibody-Enzyme Conjugate Concentrate：containing anti-hCG antibody conjugated to the enzyme horseradish peroxidase in a protein-based(BSA) buffer with a  non-mercury preservative.
TMB Chromogen Solution：containing a solution of tetramethylbenzidine (TMB) in citrate buffer with hydrogen peroxide.
Wash Concentrate：containing buffered saline with a nonionic detergent.
Stopping Solution：containing 0.2 M Sulfuric acid.
